Windows Scheduled Tasks

The framework should expose a single orchestrator (Invoke-SentinelGRC.ps1) with parameters, and Task Scheduler simply calls it with the appropriate mode.

Schedule	Task	Runtime
Every 6 hours	Inventory	2–5 minutes
Daily	Compliance Checks	5–15 minutes
Daily	Nessus Import	<1 minute
Daily	STIG Import	<1 minute
Daily	SCAP Import	<1 minute
Weekly	Executive Reports	2–5 minutes
Weekly	Database Maintenance	<1 minute


